data.description:
Stunning home that is completely remodeled.  First floor features custom porcelain tile floors. First floor bedroom and 3/4 bath. Kitchen with granite counters and custom center island. Hand crafted breakfast bar and coffee bar. First floor laundry. Second floor has custom hardwood floors. Master bath has large walk in shower with soaking tub and walk in closet. Heated three car garage is being used as a game room and adds over 1200 additional square feet of living area. New roof, two propane furnaces, two central air conditioner units. Deck, hot tub, firepit. Property boarders State Game Lands. 
Please see attached list for a complete list of renovations.
